Here's Zipcar.

00:08:10.660 --> 00:08:13.340
This is car rental
without the countertops,

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:16.420
the agents,
the parking lots or any of that stuff.

00:08:16.700 --> 00:08:20.650
It lets people find the nearest
available Zipcar and reserve it.

00:08:20.700 --> 00:08:24.780
And then as you walk towards
the vehicle and get nearby,

00:08:24.780 --> 00:08:28.700
the app displays a key fob so you can
unlock the doors and honk the horn.

00:08:28.700 --> 00:08:30.500
That's awesome!

00:08:30.680 --> 00:08:32.700
It's great apps like
this that get noticed.

00:08:32.700 --> 00:08:37.700
And here's a fantastic new app that
recently appeared on the App Store.

00:08:37.870 --> 00:08:40.700
It's called Word Lens by Quest Visual.

